OL,6,FA man who helped rescue children
OL,7,Ftrapped when their school bus
OL,8,Foverturned in Co Down has described
OL,9,Fthe moment he came across the crash.
OL,11,FFour children were taken by ambulance
OL,12,Fto hospital and more than 40 were
OL,13,Ftreated in the emergency department of
OL,14,Fthe Ulster Hospital following the
OL,15,Fincident on the Ballyblack Road East
OL,16,Fnear Carrowdore on Monday afternoon.
OL,18,FGary Smyth told UTV how he used a
OL,19,Fhammer from his van to break the bus
OL,20,Fwindows to help free the pupils inside.
