OL,6,FHe said: "It was quiet until we got
OL,7,Fdown, then we could hear the screams
OL,8,Finside the bus. The wee girls and wee
OL,9,Ffellas were terrified.
OL,11,F"We got a hammer out of the van and we
OL,12,Fshattered the glass, pulled half of it
OL,13,Fup and just jumped in and tried to get
OL,14,Fthe kids out.
OL,16,F"It was just on instinct. It's just
OL,17,Fsomething you don't want to see, you
OL,18,Fdidn't know what you were walking into
OL,19,Fand that was the problem."
