OL,6,FThe bus was carrying Strangford
OL,7,FIntegrated College pupils to Bangor
OL,8,Fwhen it crashed and ended up on its
OL,9,Fside in a field.
OL,11,FEducation Minister Paul Givan visited
OL,12,Fthe college on Tuesday to offer his
OL,13,Fsupport. He said an investigation
OL,14,Fwould now be carried out into the
OL,15,Fcrash.
