OL,6,F"I know like many people, when we
OL,7,Fwitnessed the scene, it was a shock
OL,8,Ffor us all but Mrs Foster (school
OL,9,Fprincipal Clare Foster) and the school
OL,10,Fhave been living that experience and
OL,11,Fproviding exceptional support to the
OL,12,Ffamilies and the pupils over the past
OL,13,F24 hours.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts first and foremost are
OL,16,Fwith all the families that have been
OL,17,Fimpacted. It is a parent's worst
OL,18,Fnightmare to get a call or to find out
OL,19,Fon social media that there has been
OL,20,Fthis incident."
