OL,6,FMeanwhile in the Stormont Assembly,
OL,7,FStrangford MLA Nick Mathison said is a
OL,8,F"miracle" no one was killed in the
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,F"My thoughts are with all those
OL,12,Fimpacted," he said. "It's a miracle
OL,13,Fwe're not dealing with a fatality or
OL,14,Ffatalities today in our reflections on
OL,15,Fthis issue.
OL,17,F"I think when we all saw the news
OL,18,Ffootage yesterday I think we all
OL,19,Ffeared the worst so we should be very
OL,20,Fgrateful we are not dealing with an
OL,21,Fabsolute tragedy."
