OL,6,FPolice are investigating the
OL,7,Fcircumstances behind the crash, as a
OL,8,Fmother of one of the child passengers
OL,9,Fon the double-decker said she heard
OL,10,Fpupils screaming in fear when her son
OL,11,Fcalled her.
OL,13,FThe Northern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,14,Fsaid 43 people and a driver were on
OL,15,Fthe vehicle when it crashed in Co Down.
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland's public transport
OL,18,Fprovider Translink has said it is
OL,19,Fassisting police with their
OL,20,Finvestigation.
