OL,6,FThe bus had been carrying pupils from
OL,7,FStrangford College to Bangor.
OL,9,FEmergency services and a specialist
OL,10,Frescue team attended the scene on
OL,11,FMonday afternoon where the double-
OL,12,Fdecker ended on its side in a field.
OL,14,FTwo people were rescued from the bus
OL,15,Fby firefighters using specialist
OL,16,Fcutting equipment at the scene near
OL,17,FCarrowdore.
