OL,6,FStrangford College principal Clare
OL,7,FFoster said a critical incident
OL,8,Fresponse team will assist pupils
OL,9,Ffollowing the crash.
OL,11,FShe said: "This has been a very
OL,12,Fdifficult and distressing experience
OL,13,Ffor the pupils, their families and the
OL,14,Fwider school community.
OL,16,F"The emergency services were at the
OL,17,Fscene and we would like to thank
OL,18,Feveryone who assisted for their quick
OL,19,Factions, including a number of staff
OL,20,Fand parents who provided support and
OL,21,Ffirst aid."
