OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Ambulance, which
OL,7,Fdeclared a major incident, treated and
OL,8,Fdischarged 33 people at the scene.
OL,10,FFour children were taken to hospital
OL,11,Fwith non-life-threatening injuries and
OL,12,Fseveral other patients self-presented
OL,13,Fat Ulster Hospital.
OL,15,FThe PSNI said a casualty centre was
OL,16,Fset up at Strangford College but added
OL,17,Fthat all children had either returned
OL,18,Fhome or were taken to hospital.
