OL,6,FBy Monday night, the South Eastern
OL,7,FHealth Trust said the major incident
OL,8,Fresponse had ended but teams continued
OL,9,Fto treat patients at Ulster Hospital.
OL,11,FTranslink chief executive Chris Conway
OL,12,Fconfirmed that an Ulsterbus service
OL,13,Fcarrying school pupils had crashed,
OL,14,Fadding that no other vehicles were
OL,15,Finvolved.
OL,17,FThe Ballyblack Road is to remain
OL,18,Fclosed while the PSNI investigates.
